  <brief_title>Bioequivalence Study of Capsule and Tablet Formulations of TA-8995</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I, Randomised, Open-label Cross-over Bioequivalence Study of Capsule and Tablet Formulations of TA-8995 in Healthy Male Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
