  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the pharmacokinetics of capsule and tablet
      formulations of TA-8995 in healthy male subjects aged 18 to 55 years.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
